body:
hey all! Just started getting back into the minecraft scene.

I tried digging up my old favourite minecraft servers and managed to find that this server is still up! I loved playing what I recall was called Nebula which was basically DTM.

Some Stuff About me:


  • I'm 14 years young.
  • Play CS:GO (I am Gold Nova 2 atm)
  • I play division 2 basketball
  • I'm an aussie ;)
  • It's been 3 years since i've played Minecraft and I bet i'll still kick your butt :3

Thanks for reading!

-PepeDoge
